2.00	Mike_Rice_(basketball)	Mike Rice (basketball)	Mike Rice is a National Basketball Association color commentator, one half of the Portland Trail Blazers' television broadcasting team. A former player and coach, Rice holds the distinction of being the only broadcaster ever ejected from an NBA game.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/83/Rice-Mike.jpg/300px-Rice-Mike.jpg
